data.description: Great three bedroom two bath home. Spacious living area with fireplace, in much sought after Choctaw Trails addition. Close to shopping, restaurants, and easy commute to Tinker Air Force Base. Home has new roof, fresh paint interior and exterior and new guttering and a new garage door. Home is on a corner lot. Wonderful home just waiting for new owners. Great schools close by. This one, won't last long.
